Poetry - Environment Inspection

Manage dependencies in your Python project with [bold]poetry[/bold]. Use the [bold]env[/bold] subcommand to explore the [cyan]venv[/cyan].

[dim]# Environment information[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry env info[/bold]                    [dim]# Show environment information[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry env activate[/bold]                    [dim]# Activate virtualenv[/dim]

[dim]# Configuring virtualenv location[/dim]
[bold green]$[/bold green] [bold]poetry config[/bold] [cyan]virtualenvs.in-project[/cyan] [yellow]true[/yellow]
